    "abstract": "<jats:title>Summary</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  Pregnant women were excluded from initial clinical trials for COVID-19 vaccines\n                  <jats:sup>1\u20132</jats:sup>\n                  , thus the immunologic response to vaccination in pregnancy and the transplacental transfer of maternal antibodies are just beginning to be studied\n                  <jats:sup>4\u20135</jats:sup>\n                  .\n                </jats:p>",
